<div id="content">
  <article>

    <h1>Joost Kok in Trouw on operation and future of smartwatches</h1>
    <time datetime="2018-01-08">
         08 January 2018</time>
    <p class="intro">In Dutch newspaper Trouw, Joost Kok describes the operation and accuracy of smartphones, smart bracelets and watches.</p>

    <div class="indent">

      <p>Research among top athletes and elderly shows that better results are obtained when the devices are personally tuned and give advice on when and how to move.</p>

<p>Read the article (in Dutch) in Trouw: <a href="https://www.trouw.nl/home/test-hoe-goed-werken-die-slimme-armbanden-eigenlijk-~afadb687/">Hoe goed werken die slimme armbanden eigenlijk?</a></p>

<pre>

